OL,3,CMore families due to join largest
OL,4,Cmaternity review in NHS history
OL,6,F"In the next couple of weeks I'm
OL,7,Fexpecting as chair to receive contact
OL,8,Fdetails for another 70 families that
OL,9,Fthe trust have assessed are part of
OL,10,Fthe terms of reference", explains
OL,11,FOckenden. "So I'll be writing to those
OL,12,Ffamilies as I did with previous
OL,13,Ffamilies inviting them to join the
OL,14,Freview or to let me know whether or
OL,15,Fnot they wish to opt out of the
OL,16,Freview".
OL,18,FSeven hundred staff members have also
OL,19,Fcontacted the review, with those
OL,20,Finterviews expected to start in mid-
OL,21,FApril.
